On April 21, Chinese President Xi Jinping delivered a keynote speech via video at the opening ceremony of the Boao Forum for Asia (BFA) Annual Conference 2022. Since the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China, President Xi has delivered five keynote speeches at the Boao Forum for Asia, giving the world an Asian perspective, contributing Chinese wisdom to the world and making a strong call for the building of a community with a shared future for mankind.